        "subject": "LU-13883 lnet: Lookup lpni after discovery",
        "message": "LU-13883 lnet: Lookup lpni after discovery\n\nThe lpni for a nid can change as part of the discovery process (see\nlnet_peer_add_nid()). As such, LNetPrimaryNID and lnet_discover()\nneed to lookup the lpni again after discovery completes to make sure\nthey get the correct peer.\n\nHPE-bug-id: LUS-9167\nSigned-off-by: Chris Horn <chris.horn@hpe.com>\nChange-Id: I976676f775cb26e2e8cac89649d248950e84490e\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
